                <h2>Legal Services for Irwin & North Huntingdon</h2>
                <p>Irwin and North Huntingdon Township are among Westmoreland County's most vibrant communities, with a mix of established neighborhoods, growing commercial corridors, and families who value their roots. Ament Law Group's Murrysville office is just a short drive north on Route 30 or via the Turnpike, making us an easy choice for residents who want experienced local counsel.</p>

                <h2>Estate Planning</h2>
                <p>We help Irwin and North Huntingdon families create estate plans that protect their assets and provide for their loved ones. Our services include wills, revocable living trusts, durable powers of attorney, and advance healthcare directives — all drafted to comply with Pennsylvania law and tailored to your family's circumstances.</p>

                <h2>Probate Administration</h2>
                <p>Estates in Irwin and North Huntingdon are administered through the Westmoreland County Register of Wills in Greensburg. We guide executors through every step — from obtaining Short Certificates and marshaling assets to filing Pennsylvania Inheritance Tax Returns and preparing the final accounting for Orphans' Court.</p>

